body:
I was joining a game and when i was on the loading screen, everything just froze. I had to restart my laptop and try again. After waiting for 5 mins in the loading screen  I got a message that i had been Disconnected. After I rejoined, It was 13 mins in and I played the rest of the game. I then got a leaver. People told me to do the hextech tool but whenever i click on it it asks for admin password and after I  enter it in nothing happens.

This is a long cycle that keeps going on and on and I keep having to wait 20 mins before each game for 5 games when I am really short on time.

Pls halp {{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}}
